
WISHLIST:
- use Time-based animations with "requestAnimationFrame" instead of a fixed FPS
- load all the data once at the beginning
- disable "newAttempt" button when the game is running or loading

BUGS:
- "touchstart" and "touchend" are not working on smartphones
- "preventDefault" is not working on Firefox to disable spacebar behavour
- "preventDefault" is not working on Chromium to disable double-click/double-tap

